      • getProductTypes

        public static java.lang.String[] getProductTypes()

        getProductTypes

        Description: Extracts the array from ProductType holding every description associated with a ProductType literal and returns it. The method passes on the descriptios done by ProductType.getProductTypes().

        Preconditions:

        • getProductTypes method in ProductType must be in place.

        Postconditions:

        • A String array is returned holding the descriptions of every Literal.
        Returns:
        A string[] holding all the descriptions representing the ProductType literals.

      • getName

        public java.lang.String getName()

        getName

        Description: Allows the extraction of the name from a Product instance as a String.

        Preconditions:

        • Null search can't be done on a null object. Null Pointer Exception.

        Postconditions:

        • A String containing the name of a Product instance is returned.
        Returns:
        A String with the name of a Product instance.
